MOST IMMEDIATE
No.1/34/1/2001-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 8th February, 2001.
19 Magha, 1922(S).
The undersigned is directed to
say that with effect from the 7th February,
2001 :-
i)
Shri N.T. Shanmugam relinquished the charge of the office of Minister
of State (Independent charge) of the Ministry of Coal; and
Shri E. Ponnuswamy relinquished the charge of the office of Minister
of State in the Ministry of Petroleum and Natural Gas.
ii)
(P.'Gopalakrishnan)
for Cabinet Secretary
Tele : 3015802

Members of the
Planning Commission.
(P Gopalakrishnan)
